WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.350
What did the Lord show me last night

00:00:01.360 --> 00:00:03.429
concerning Donald Trump? I saw him at a

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:05.910
ballroom party. I saw him; he was

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.230
celebrating. He had a tuxedo on.

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.549
They were all dressed up,

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:12.870
but he had a goblet, a glass in

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:16.630
his hand. I did not

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:19.269
see anybody putting anything in his

00:00:19.279 --> 00:00:23.429
glass. I

00:00:23.439 --> 00:00:25.509
don't add to or take away from anything

00:00:25.519 --> 00:00:29.429
in a vision. I saw a glass in his hand

00:00:29.439 --> 00:00:33.030
and it was focused on this glass.

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:35.190
I don't want to add; like I

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.270
said, you add to it and you get flaky. Don't.

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:38.790
This is what I saw. I saw him holding

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.110
the glass and then I saw him having a

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:43.190
massive heart attack. I saw something

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:48.470
wrong in his heart. I

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:48.480
saw

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:51.510
the

00:00:51.510 --> 00:00:51.520
waitstaff

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.830
and I don't know what happened between

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:57.350
the glass and the goblet and him, why he

00:00:57.360 --> 00:00:59.349
would do this, but he was holding it. Now,

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:01.430
all the doctors say he's okay, but he was

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:04.630
holding a drink and I saw the drink and

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:07.270
the vision was focused on

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:10.390
that cup. The Lord said, 'Pray over his

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:14.230
food. Pray over his drink. Pray over the

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:16.870
parties.

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:19.030
Pray over him as he has these

00:01:19.040 --> 00:01:20.630
get-togethers.'So,

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:24.070
instantaneously, you can add to it

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:25.510
and say, 'Well, that's probably they're

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:26.630
going to try to poison him.'I don't

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:28.630
know. That's not what the

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:32.550
Lord said. All I saw was a cup with

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:35.190
gold and I saw the drink and I saw the

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.190
food and I saw the party and I saw

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.910
everybody dressed up and then I saw him

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:43.270
taking it to his lips.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:47.429
And then he went down. So, does that

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:49.910
mean the poison is in his glass? I

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:51.910
don't know. I can't answer that.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:53.190
But the Lord said, 'Pray over his

00:01:53.190 --> 00:01:53.200
drink.'Then

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:57.990
I saw Don Jr. again with

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.469
the white outfit on with flashes and him

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:02.950
being shot in the chest. I saw praying

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:04.950
over his son.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.670
He was at a party and event again. And

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.550
then I saw the Secret Service; he said pray

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:13.910
for their attentiveness even at a party.

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:17.030
Pray for their attentiveness.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:18.470
Watching the crowd, watching his

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:20.229
surroundings, praying for protection

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:23.990
over him and his family.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:27.030
So that's what we do.

00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:30.229
Interceding for Donald Trump, for him to

00:02:30.239 --> 00:02:32.470
live long and finish strong and finish

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.390
what God has called him to do, that no

00:02:34.400 --> 00:02:37.350
weapon formed against him will prosper,

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:39.990
or his children, because it would cause

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.229
great grief and he would not... I'm telling

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:44.229
you I've seen the outcome of what

00:02:44.239 --> 00:02:47.990
happens whenever his son was fatally

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.990
wounded

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:53.350
and the Lord said to me, 'You must pray

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:57.110
for his children's safety.'He was so

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.270
grieving, grief-stricken, he could not

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:03.190
function the rest of the term

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:07.030
because he was grieving

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.670
so much for the loss of his

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:11.750
son. He was not able to even

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:15.270
hardly walk and I saw Melania. I

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:17.990
remember I told you all I saw his

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.990
daughter dressed up in solid black and

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.910
they were going to the

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:23.509
funeral service where the

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:26.470
inauguration was there by the White

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:28.309
House, that church, it was like

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.949
a big church service like that. And they

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:32.949
were going to this service and

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:34.869
there were people from everywhere. And I

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:36.630
saw him walking down and he got out of

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:39.509
the Beast and he was walking down and I

00:03:39.519 --> 00:03:42.390
remember him walking to the funeral

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:45.270
reception, the service, and he was

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:47.270
weeping.

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:49.509
He was weeping.

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.390
He could not keep himself held up. They

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:56.149
were helping him walk. It was awful.

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:58.550
So when I have that stern of a

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:00.229
vision, if I see something that clear,

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:02.550
I've not stopped praying since.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.789
Interceding for the protection of Don

00:04:04.799 --> 00:04:09.990
Jr., over Kai, over Eric, over

00:04:09.990 --> 00:04:10.000
Barron,

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:14.869
over all of them, Tiffany, over Ivanka,

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:17.990
that God's hand would be on their family

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.469
and on his marriage. So that's what we

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:22.629
do. We continue to do this. And I saw an

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:25.909
attack against his buildings more than

00:04:25.919 --> 00:04:29.110
once now.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:31.510
I keep seeing them

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.590
trying to attack his main

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.830
attractions, you know, his Trump

00:04:35.840 --> 00:04:38.790
towers and hotels and golf courses and

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:41.110
just interceding because of the plans to

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:43.830
try to rob him financially. But not only

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:45.830
that, that caused a distraction to this

00:04:45.840 --> 00:05:07.188
nation by hurting his assets.

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:18.870
Where is this place?

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:25.670
I see white drapes.

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:29.189
I see chandeliers. He's

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.510
wearing a black tie. He's wearing a

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:34.390
black tuxedo again.

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:37.270
I see the tuxedo. He has

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.830
something in his hand. Looks like a

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:43.990
drink. We know Trump

00:05:43.990 --> 00:05:44.000
doesn't

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.710
drink alcohol. I see

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:50.070
this glass that has gold

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:53.350
at the top. There's gold at the top of

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:55.990
this glass. That's actual real gold.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.870
It's like a golden glass, a goblet like

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:01.830
fine crystal. There's

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:05.350
white tablecloths. There's white tables

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:07.670
with beautiful centerpiece

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:09.909
arrangements.

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.909
These women are

00:06:13.919 --> 00:06:16.870
dressed up in ball gowns. Men are in

00:06:16.870 --> 00:06:16.880
black

00:06:16.880 --> 00:06:18.629
tuxedos. They're all dressed up

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:21.029
very nice. We pray a protection over

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:24.070
President Trump. We pray over him. We

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:26.950
pray over his sons. We pray over his

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:29.270
daughters. We pray over his family.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:31.909
We pray a hedge of

00:06:31.919 --> 00:06:34.629
protection around and about them, over

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:38.309
every party, over every

00:06:38.309 --> 00:06:38.319
get-together,

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:41.430
any kind of celebration. We pray a hedge

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:45.110
of protection that his Secret Service

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:47.909
is more attentive even to the ones that

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:50.390
are in the room.

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:52.710
Just because they pass security, the

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:57.270
ones in the room...

00:06:57.280 --> 00:07:00.790
I don't understand it

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.510
in the natural. We thank you Lord that

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:05.830
President Trump is protected.

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:16.150
No

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:18.870
weapon formed against him would prosper.

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:23.110
Every plot, every plan will be uncovered

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:27.270
in the name of Jesus, at

00:07:27.270 --> 00:07:27.280
black-tie

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:31.270
events. We

00:07:31.270 --> 00:07:31.280
pray

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:35.110
over Don Jr.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:40.950
The blood

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:43.430
of Jesus surround him

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:46.629
in

00:07:49.189 --> 00:07:49.199
Jesus'name.

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:54.390
He will finish

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.670
his course. He will live long and finish

00:07:57.680 --> 00:08:01.430
strong. We pray over his heart,

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:07.270
over every artery, over

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.670
the valves of the

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:13.029
heart. We call protection in the name of

00:08:13.039 --> 00:08:15.029
Jesus

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:17.430
over drinks.

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:23.350
We pray over the food. We bless

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.029
his food. I believe we can pray

00:08:25.029 --> 00:08:25.039
over

00:08:25.039 --> 00:08:27.189
his food.

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:33.110
I pray over his

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:36.870
drink and the goblet.

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:40.070
We pray over his drinks,

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.990
over everything that is ever handed to

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:46.230
him.

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:56.230
You said we could eat or

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:58.949
drink any deadly thing and it would not

00:08:58.959 --> 00:09:02.070
harm us.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:05.350
Everything we drink, everything we eat,

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:08.070
we thank you Lord.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:12.389
You see that it affects the heart. Like

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:15.590
everything we drink,

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:18.150
everything he eats,

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:20.870
he's protected.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:35.430
I

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:38.949
pray over him as he drinks these things.

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:41.430
That Father, any kind of poison, any kind

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:44.790
of thing, nothing comes nigh,

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:49.030
even to make it look like an

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:53.990
accident,

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:56.470
like

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.269
it's just natural.

00:10:07.839 --> 00:10:11.030
Every plot, every plan, every pursuit. I

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:12.630
thank you, Lord, that you protect

00:10:12.640 --> 00:10:15.590
President Trump.

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.269
That you raise up a hedge around and

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:19.590
about him. Father,

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.829
I thank you that his Secret Service are

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:25.670
so heightened and alert,

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:28.710
they never let

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:30.630
their guard down. They are like

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:34.870
a bulldog the whole time. Always

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:37.509
watching everybody's hands, always

00:10:37.519 --> 00:10:40.069
watching the people who are bringing

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:43.190
refreshments.

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:45.110
Whoever is over that, I thank you Lord

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:46.790
that they're smart,

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.030
they're watching over what he eats

00:10:49.030 --> 00:10:49.040
and

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:51.509
what he drinks.

00:10:56.640 --> 00:10:59.509
They must not

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:03.350
become lax;

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:05.350
they must protect our President. I

00:11:05.350 --> 00:11:05.360
pray over

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:09.750
Mar-a-Lago. I

00:11:09.750 --> 00:11:09.760
pray over

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:13.829
any events, over

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:16.470
his family,

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:21.030
over Don Jr.,

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:24.150
over Kai, even over Barron, even over

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:26.870
this boy.

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:30.310
We pray a hedge around and

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:32.790
about his son that the Kennedy curse

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:35.519
would be broken.

